                  </hi>. These are both bad.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The Prisoner's Statement before the Magistrate:</hi>—"I say that I never did</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186706100050"></xptr>
               <p>give that gentleman (Carroll) the shilling at all. He did not see my face. I should have had the change out of the shilling."</p>
